name: Yvette D'Entremont
bio: Sweary scientist, but I mostly do that elsewhere.

social_posts.post_text: I’m turning 40 this year. It’ll be okay.
So I broke a finger and was treated for MRSA in one week. Maybe chainsaw juggling in an infectious disease lab was ill-advised.
I’m turning 40 next month and my hair started growing in curly this year. Well then. I guess we’re doing the next half a little different.
Ruby has mastered the art of “now let’s take a silly one.” #dogsofinstagram #kelpies
Families can be… complicated. #havethefathersdayyoudeserve💁🏾‍♀️
These two are about to drop their hottest new album, “I horked it up but it still has a flavor.” #dogsofinstagram

I’m at Disneyland with SciRoomie for her birthday (no picture of roomie per her request). No MOS today because priorities.

If you spot me, don’t be a stranger!

It’s easy to remain convinced I got out of grad school last week until something reminds me that my twenties are not as close as they appear in my rear view. It was a good day, but I gotta leave 8am-midnight Disney-ing to the kids. #notquiteadisneyadult
It’s SciDog’s house, I just bend myself into a chair here. #tinydogs #dogsofinstagram #ehlersdanlos

I accept your judgement on my unkempt pillow assembly (new band name), but I also come asking… wtf should I do with the overhead view in the second picture? As we say in theatre, I used the goddamn space and made the closet into a cocoon-esque head space for my bed. Now I’m left with vestigial closet… things… for the view before I fall asleep. It’s gotten better as I’ve added lighting and a fabric backdrop but it still feels empty and weird at the moment. Twinkle lights? Hidden Mickeys? More drapery shit? Ropes of unmentionable nature? It probably won’t be glow in the dark stars but I make no promises. #decoratelikeapro #decoratelikeimclueless
I still have a week. #older #itbeatsthealternative

A 40th birthday spent running around LA on a pussy hunt… ahem, picking up my cat, along with the rest of my shit from my ex’s place. I’m so grateful to my friends who threw their heavy lifting into this, it was a lot of work. My stuff is everywhere, I’m exhausted, but my baby cat Lexi seems happy to be home. I may have cried when I got her out of the carrier and into my room. #SciKitty
How I spent my summer vacation. #doghouse

Finish recording a podcast and only then did I realize that my hair has been performing a silent protest against gravity for the last two hours. Nobody warned me about this physics defying absurdity when my hair started forming ringlets six months ago. #curlyhairdontcare

After receiving an invite the highly exclusive morning dog meeting, my day easily went downhill from there. 

You could even say it was… ruff? I’ll see myself out.
Unpacking and finding places for everything has been difficult. Fortunately I found a place to store my $20 wedding dress. #burnitdown
Buddy, enough with your kvetching, I didn’t particularly want it up the nostril either. #dogsofinstagram #ithasaflavor
And in the morning, we rally with our fellow workers. #hotlaborsummer

My roommate is #WGA, and this morning I joined her for an early rally to support the #teamsters. If they don’t have a new contract negotiated by July 31st, 340,000 workers will go on strike. Welcome to #hotlaborsummer. #wgastrong #sagaftrastrong
We caught a SpaceX launch from our backyard last night. It was pretty spectacular.

SciRoomie: “I feel like crap, mind if we go see Barbie tomorrow?”
Me: “nah, but I am going to finish my makeup for instagram.” To be fair, it needs to be far more colorful for this movie. Third picture because I am incorrigible. #barbenheimer #barbie #makeupaddict #derpface

Come on Barbies, let’s go…. To sleep soon but first pictures! NH girlies night out for a movie that was better than it had any right to be. Go see the Barbie movie, it was incredible. Didn’t miss a goddamn note. #barbie #girlsnight #butfirstmakeup #thenderpface

I thought I should spend more time writing in my bedroom because I wanted to make sure my babygirl Lexi wasn’t overheating in this hellscape. Nope. Somehow, she found the warmest spot in the room (right between me and the keyboard) and decided it needed a Lexi-shaped blanket. I missed her. #catfitscatsits #catsofinstagram #tortitude

I left the house twice in a week for things I haven’t done since the before times. I’m starting to think my 40s are gonna be just fine. Now… what should I sing at karaoke next week? #musicaltheatrekid

And today we support strikes. 

For labor. 
And against the Mariners. #wgastrong #wgastrike
One of these goofballs got a year older. An appropriate number of brain cells were sacrificed for the cause. #itwasanightout #thisis40
For the MOS today, I reviewed my friend Brian’s new documentary, The UFO Movie THEY Don’t Want You To See. You should see it.

100 days of striking. Come join us at Universal. 

#HotLaborSummer 
#WGAStrong
#PayYourWriters 
#PayYourActors
Ma’am, we heard you were having a case of the weepies. We’re both here for snuggles, but the cat will be judging you the whole time. #petsofinstagram

Hurricane Hilary is coming. I’m occasionally on The Weather Channel, so you can trust my ramblings about it. 

#hurricanehilary #socalweather #climatechange 
https://rb.gy/vyazw
We’ll sweat it off soon. #prompicket #wgastrong

“Can I hear a little commotion for the dress?” Avoiding a wardrobe malfunction involved tape and prayer. Worth it. Back to it again next week. (Photo credit first three shots: @b.side.photography) 

#wgastrong #wgastrike
Daytime look vs. nighttime look. Picketing your local streaming service, then home for live-streaming. Probably a long shower in between. #jewnionstrong #wgastrike #almostalivestreamer

It might be the curls, but every so often a picture shows up in which I look so, so much like my brother. 

Miss that kid.
*heavy sigh* #minusone
I have better tits in the apocalypse, per our AI overlords.

Being addressed as Mr. Stark or just “Tony” all day has been a trip. Leo used to cosplay as Tony Stark. When I get the chance to do genius-billionaire-playboy-philanthropist cosplay, it feels like stepping into Leo’s shoes for just a bit. I’m looking forward to scrubbing my face before I accidentally rub this mess everywhere though.
Long Beach Comic Con, it’s been a blast.

Not a paid ad, just met fellow Tony Stark facial hair aficionado @davidfstarr this weekend at #LBCC. He wrote and illustrated this beautiful children’s science book (which I’ll be gifting every time one of my friends has a little one who’s starting to get curious about science). Check it out: https://www.babyanimalscientistsaz.com

Last night at karaoke: 
“You look like something out of a film noir.” 
“Well then I need pictures.” *hands phone to stranger for impromptu photoshoot* #iwasamodelonce
SciRoomie is out of town so the dogs are being weirder. I’m always this weird. #dogsofinstagram #kelpie #pompom
Like mother like Lexi. #catsofinstagram #torties #tortitude

Quantum aromatherapy.
Quantum. Fucking. Aromatherapy. 
A PhFuckingD in Quantum Fucking Aromatherapy. 

Fuck you and the unaccredited degree mill you rode in on, “doctor” Cécile Ellert.

#justaddquantum #pseudoscience #utternonsense #bullshit #brandolinislaw
For last minute plans, it’ll suffice somehow. #whereami

This was a year ago today at Mom’s house. A few hours later I had my first positive covid test. I ended up staying for a month. Time for a booster before any more hijinks, that was miserable. #boostershot #covidvacccine #vaccineswork #longcovid

It’s that time of year again- I got my flu shot and covid booster on Thursday. I was moving at the speed of nope on Friday. Back to human with a double dose of nanobots today.
#weredoingshots #covidbooster #flushot
I missed this human’s perfect face.
Why is it always chapstick? Because cats. #catsofinstagram
I leave the house occasionally. One day I’ll learn to come home by a sensible hour. Today was not that day. #karaoke

I’m having an excellent hair day. 

But I would like to know when curly hair starts getting longer instead of just… bigger. #curlyhairdontcare

Impossibly, the kinds of things that would ruin straight hair only make curls bigger and better through the day. It’s been many hours and approximately a wind tunnel worth of fuckery since this picture and it’s like they’re developing into their final form. #curlyhairdontcare #yesimobsessed

I cleverly avoided Black Friday shopping today by visiting local NH landmarks. I wasn’t the only one- a family arrived just before us that drove three hours to take a few pictures, and kindly offered me these definitely very real swords for pictures (ahem). Oddly there’s a plaque to go along with the manhole cover that’s now planted somewhere else in town and this was all the cold I could handle today. Weekend adventure? #80sbaby #TMNT

I’m a few days late, but I made this. Thing about avoiding gluten is that most gluten free pie crusts suck, so I turn them into giant cookies which do not suck. This crust was made of ginger snaps and pecans for a bourbon pecan pie. It was perfectly sinful. #thankfulthedishesaredone
My roommate has a new boyfriend. So I’m finding new surprises in the fridge.
Write every story under the sun about marsupials, still going on health podcasts playing SciBabe’s greatest hits: debunking nutrition myths.
*sigh* fine, Buddy. We finish writing about Hubble tomorrow. #momentofscience
Buddy and Ruby are watching their favorite show, Pyromania 7.

I must have missed the verse in the Twelve Days of Christmas about fluffy cuddly loquacious pink cockatoos. Rosie was snuggle drunk on my shoulder for a while yesterday and now I might want a bird. Best Christmas I’ve had in LA. Thanks for having us @avensobrien and thanks for bringing bird-dog @ashogunnameddavid.

Check out my last article of the year, it’s a big old debunking extravaganza including MBTI, Dunning Kruger, Love Languages, the Bystander Effect, and the old “we only use 10% of our brains” myth that just won’t quit. 
(And sign up for my patreon to get every article delivered to your inbox… and because these things just don’t write themselves)

It’s going to be in the 30s here in North Hollywood tonight. I will be remaining under this pillow fort until further notice. #nopedegreesoutside
